{"title":"北戴河之冬（二首）","authors":["纪学"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北戴河之冬（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不会被忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"候鸟似的游人星散了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给你一片冷寞阒寂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那绵软滚烫的沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那捏得出笑语的空气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光下的花花绿绿帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及帐篷下湿润的曲线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都随着秋风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘然远去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只能默默咀嚼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的记忆——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情侣的双双倩影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的歪歪斜斜的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人汗湿的情趣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太喜欢热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会无端染上愁绪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去了的就去了吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必苦苦相思？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天还属于你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水还属于你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带咸味的海风还属于你……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美不能消灭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然有时遭到冷落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但不会被忘记！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果仅仅为了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廉价的赞誉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又何必作这样的选择！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不屈服于风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风要将我撕碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪也助风，想把我吞噬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难地张开翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔，向着认定的远方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管风浪无情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把无数生命化为礁石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上，仍然有勇敢者！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}